#  Simple Calculator

A modern calculator built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript.

## ✨ Features
- Addition, Subtraction, Multiplication, Division
- Decimal support
- Division by zero handling
- Keyboard support
- Clean UI design
- Error handling

## ⌨️ Keyboard Shortcuts
- Numbers: 0–9
- Operators: + - * /
- Enter: Calculate
- Backspace: Delete
- Esc: Clear

## 🚀 How to Run

1. Clone the repository:
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/simple-calculator.git

2. Open folder in VS Code

3. Open `index.html`

4. Use Live Server or open directly in browser

## 🌍 Deploy on GitHub Pages

Go to:
Settings → Pages → Deploy from main branch → root

Your calculator will be live online!
